These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, swisher, game
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, gardening, collecting
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, roller, taxi
House: cape-cod, wooden, modern
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, august, june
3 different games are played: bridge, billiard, domino
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, amber, apricot
 1. the modern house is the person driving the taxi##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 3. the dannemann-smoker is the person driving the roller##1
 4. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
 5. the person who likes brown is the wooden house##1
 6. the cape-cod house is on the right of the modern house##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is the game-smoker##1
10. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |    3     |
| Cigar      | dannemann  | swisher   | game      |
| Hobby          | collecting      | writing     | gardening     |
| Transport           | roller | taxi  | airplane   |
| House   | wooden   | modern     | cape-cod  |
| Birthday   | november      | august      | june      |
| Game   | domino      | billiard    | bridge   |
| Color         | brown    | amber | apricot |

