3 different games are played: whist, bridge, snooker
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, december, may
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, daisy, azalea
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, blend, bolivar
City: london, san-francisco, hamburg
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of hip-hop is the baccarat-smoker##1
 3. the person traveling to san-francisco is in the middle##1
 4. the fan of punk is the person who growsazalea##1
 5. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
 7. the bolivar-smoker is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of punk is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
10. the person drinking cola is the person who growslily##1
11. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Music-Genre         | punk | hip-hop  | salsa     |
| Beverage           | coffee        | milk | cola    |
| Game   | bridge  | snooker    | whist    |
| Birthday   | may    | december    | october   |
| Flower           | azalea        | daisy    | lily        |
