.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-17::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, bus, trike
3 different games are played: monopoly, poker, domino
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, dahlia, azalea
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, ebony, ivory
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, blend, oliveros
City: prague, san-francisco, berlin
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, snake, rat
 1. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
 2. the person who likes ebony is the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the person driving the trike is the person playing monopoly##1
 4. the owner of the chinchilla is the blend-smoker##1
 5. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 6. the person who growsdahlia is the oliveros-smoker##1
 7. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 8. the person traveling to berlin is in the middle##1
 9. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
10. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
11. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |       3        |
| Transport      | trike   | train        | bus           |
| Game         | monopoly | domino          | poker      |
| Flower           | zinnia   | dahlia | azalea |
| Color   | ebony  | white       | ivory         |
| Cigar   | blend    | oliveros          | ritmeester        |
| City   | san-francisco  | berlin        | prague     |
| Pet         | chinchilla   | rat         | snake       |

