.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-18::.
House: tower, wooden, cape-cod
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, italian, canadian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, prince, baccarat
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, fuchsia, blood-red
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, mouse, pony
City: new-york, edinburgh, miami
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, marigold, amaryllis
 1. the person who growsmarigold is the prince-smoker##1
 2. the person traveling to edinburgh is the prince-smoker##1
 3. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 4. the egyptian is on the far right##1
 5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 6. the baccarat-smoker is the tower house##1
 7. the cape-cod house is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
 8. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 9. the person who likes blue is on the right of the italian##1
10. the wooden house is the owner of the pony##1
11. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
12. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |      3      |
| House      | tower       | cape-cod      | wooden      |
| Nationality          | italian        | canadian | egyptian   |
| Cigar         | baccarat       | prince    | havana  |
| Color           | blood-red | blue     | fuchsia    |
| Pet   | goldfish       | mouse   | pony |
| City         | miami        | edinburgh   | new-york     |
| Flower     | amaryllis          | marigold       | poppy         |

