.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-19::.
House: townhouse, modern, colonial
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing, traveling
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, dahlia, poppy
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, car, quad-bike
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, april, november
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, bongani, davidoff
3 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, chess
 1. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
 2. the colonial house is in the middle##1
 3. the game-smoker is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 5. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is the bongani-smoker##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
10. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| House      | modern      | colonial         | townhouse |
| Hobby          | rock-climbing | traveling        | puzzles   |
| Flower   | zinnia | dahlia       | poppy   |
| Transport   | airplane   | quad-bike          | car       |
| Birthday   | april  | november      | june   |
| Cigar           | davidoff    | bongani        | game        |
| Game         | chess  | scrabble | monopoly     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-20::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, dannemann, bolivar
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, volleyball, sailing
House: modern, tower, colonial
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, project-manager, accountant
3 different games are played: poker, scrabble, whist
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, orange, purple
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, november, march
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 2. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 3. the dancer is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the accountant##1
 5. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 6. the colonial house is the person who likes green##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who likes green##1
 8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 9. the person playing whist is in the middle##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is in the middle##1
11. the modern house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3      |
| Cigar      | dannemann       | baccarat     | bolivar         |
| Sport          | volleyball      | weightlifting  | sailing     |
| House         | modern | tower     | colonial |
| Job   | dancer  | accountant | project-manager     |
| Game   | poker    | whist      | scrabble     |
| Color   | orange  | purple    | green  |
| Birthday           | june   | march      | november      |

 